n or any part thereof as a basis for the design or creation of any method, system, apparatus or device similar to any method, system, apparatus or device embodied in the Confidential Information unless expressly authorized in writing by Disclosing Party; and\n(h) Utilize the best efforts possible to protect and safeguard the Confidential\nInformation from loss, theft, destruction, or the like.\n\n3.", "mimetype": "text/plain", "start_char_idx": 2697, "end_char_idx": 3134, "metadata_seperator": "\n", "text_template": "{metadata_str}\n\n{content}", "class_name": "TextNode"}, "__type__": "1"}, "8af2481b-05dc-4576-b8ab-0b963576fa01": {"__data__": {"id_": "8af2481b-05dc-4576-b8ab-0b963576fa01", "embedding": null, "metadata": {}, "excluded_embed_metadata_keys": [], "excluded_llm_metadata_keys": [], "relationships": {"1": {"node_id": "8d1431b8-8436-43ab-aa4e-f67eb1448bbe", "node_type": "4", "metadata": {}, "hash": "4c683a94ea810b151b5bc7a1738bc5cd9947edc5f54db75997ace58c567158a7", "class_name": "RelatedNodeInfo"}, "2": {"node_id": "896db214-938f-461c-9d3e-dd1ddba4ad68", "node_type": "1", "metadata": {}, "hash": "ebc917751c3b4a3f808df44c582035890958d388e78c087bce2a17dc2d3604ae", "class_name": "RelatedNodeInfo"}, "3": {"node_id": "2a2f0ebb-5fd6-4244-a756-a44fbbf256b1", "node_type": "1", "metadata": {}, "hash": "3b64ac1e078659287dcc4a446af2e9be6ffe1daead21973e96ad24f4417df7c5", "class_name": "RelatedNodeInfo"}}, "metadata_template": "{key}: {value}", "metadata_separator": "\n", "text": "RETURN OF CONFIDENTIAL INFORMATION\n\nAll information provided by the Disclosing Party shall remain the property of the Disclosing Party.  Receiving Party agrees to return all Confidential Information to Disclosing Party within 15 days of written demand by Disclosing Party.", "mimetype": "text/plain", "start_char_idx": 3135, "end_char_idx": 3407, "metadata_seperator": "\n", "text_template": "{metadata_str}\n\n{content}", "class_name": "TextNode"}, "__type__": "1"}, "2a2f0ebb-5fd6-4244-a756-a44fbbf256b1": {"__data__": {"id_": "2a2f0ebb-5fd6-4244-a756-a44fbbf256b1", "embedding": null, "metadata": {}, "excluded_embed_metadata_keys": [], "excluded_llm_metadata_keys": [], "relationships": {"1": {"node_id": "8d1431b8-8436-43ab-aa4e-f67eb1448bbe", "node_type": "4", "metadata": {}, "hash": "4c683a94ea810b151b5bc7a1738bc5cd9947edc5f54db75997ace58c567158a7", "class_name": "RelatedNodeInfo"}, "2": {"node_id": "8af2481b-05dc-4576-b8ab-0b963576fa01", "node_type": "1", "metadata": {}, "hash": "77fd12b815f0d674d369bce2525e3002e9ec3c5f39596d3948829e434e1c2b94", "class_name": "RelatedNodeInfo"}, "3": {"node_id": "943d670c-63c6-42d4-a273-75932cb2c863", "node_type": "1", "metadata": {}, "hash": "faa268a0f5c7c07c14bca0b2c7bf564920fe4741bdc923b673a2a476b73cb92b", "class_name": "RelatedNodeInfo"}}, "metadata_template": "{key}: {value}", "metadata_separator": "\n", "text": "When the Receiving Party has finished reviewing the information provided by the Disclosing Party and has made a decision as to whether or not to work with the Disclosing Party, Receiving Party shall return all information to the Disclosing Party without retaining any copies.\n\n4. NON-ASSIGNABLE\n\nThis agreement shall be non-assignable by the Receiving Party unless prior written consent of the Disclosing Party is received.", "mimetype": "text/plain", "start_char_idx": 3409, "end_char_idx": 3832, "metadata_seperator": "\n", "text_template": "{metadata_str}\n\n{content}", "class_name": "TextNode"}, "__type__": "1"}, "943d670c-63c6-42d4-a273-75932cb2c863": {"__data__": {"id_": "943d670c-63c6-42d4-a273-75932cb2c863", "embedding": null, "metadata": {}, "excluded_embed_metadata_keys": [], "excluded_llm_metadata_keys": [], "relationships": {"1": {"node_id": "8d1431b8-8436-43ab-aa4e-f67eb1448bbe", "node_type": "4", "metadata": {}, "hash": "4c683a94ea810b151b5bc7a1738bc5cd9947edc5f54db75997ace58c567158a7", "class_name": "RelatedNodeInfo"}, "2": {"node_id": "2a2f0ebb-5fd6-4244-a756-a44fbbf256b1", "node_type": "1", "